
                              gzstream
      C++ iostream classes wrapping the zlib compression library.
===========================================================================
TO USE THIS LIBRARY AS A SHARED OBJECT IN THE PACKET CAPTURE PRE-PROCESSOR

1) Make using the "MakefileShared" file
   
   cd /opt/ericsson/pcp/pect/pect/gzstream
   make -f MakefileShared

2) Copy the the resulting libgzstream.so to the /opt/ericsson/lib directory  
   
   cd /opt/ericsson/pcp/pect/pect/gzstream
   cp libgzstream.so /opt/ericsson/lib/

See index.html for documentation.
